window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>All of Vacuos shall know the Voidgod's wrath.</b></p> <p>Now that Guardian Angel Z357 is dead, there is nothing left standing in the path of Kallistus Kal and his one true desire. Not the Astrad Kingdom, not the Sect of the Abyssal Thorns, and certainly not Amelia. Especially not Amelia. Because she is far too busy dealing with the baby bastion bees back in her restaurant.</p> <p>However, when everyone turns to her to save them, she will have no choice but to choose between her normal life and being a hero once again.</p>"; 
